OL,3,CDevoted mum with 'vibrant soul'
OL,4,Cremembered by family after death in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,F"A beautiful, vibrant soul" is how the
OL,8,Ffamily of a woman who died in
OL,9,FLeicester will be remembered.
OL,11,FNila Patel died in hospital on
OL,12,FThursday, 26 June, following an
OL,13,Fincident in Aylestone Road two days
OL,14,Fearlier.
OL,16,FThe 53-year-old's son Jaidan Patel and
OL,17,Fdaughter Danika Patel described her as
OL,18,F"one of the most kind-hearted people
OL,19,Fyou could ever meet".
