OL,7,FA joint statement released through
OL,8,FLeicestershire Police said: "We are
OL,9,Fheartbroken, but we want the world to
OL,10,Fknow who our mum truly was - a
OL,11,Fbeautiful, vibrant soul who deserved
OL,12,Fso much more.
OL,14,F"Mum was one of the most kind-hearted
OL,15,Fpeople you could ever meet.
