OL,3,CDevoted mum with 'vibrant soul'
OL,4,Cremembered by family after death in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,F"Her love was quiet but powerful -
OL,8,Fshown through warm meals, thoughtful
OL,9,Fwords, and a smile that could light up
OL,10,Fany room. She always put others before
OL,11,Fherself, offering comfort without ever
OL,12,Fasking for anything in return.
OL,14,F"Even when life was hard, she carried
OL,15,Fon with strength, dignity and a smile
OL,16,Fon her face.
OL,18,FThe statement described her as a
OL,19,Fdevoted mother, a loyal friend, and an
OL,20,Fincredibly hard worker.
