OL,3,CDevoted mum with 'vibrant soul'
OL,4,Cremembered by family after death in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,FIt reads: "At home and in her career,
OL,8,Fshe gave everything she had - never
OL,9,Fcomplaining, always giving. She raised
OL,10,Fus with patience, love, and unwavering
OL,11,Fsupport, and our greatest wish was
OL,12,Falways to make her proud.
OL,14,F"Mum's life was full of love, and the
OL,15,Fstories we've heard from those who
OL,16,Fknew her have reminded us of just how
OL,17,Fdeeply she touched the lives around
OL,18,Fher. She was truly rich in love and
OL,19,Fgenerosity.
