OL,3,CDevoted mum with 'vibrant soul'
OL,4,Cremembered by family after death in
OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,F"We will miss her more than words can
OL,8,Fever express.
OL,10,F"We didn't get the chance to say
OL,11,Fgoodbye, and that pain is something we
OL,12,Fcarry every day. But we will continue
OL,13,Fto speak her name with pride, honour
OL,14,Fher memory, and live by the values she
OL,15,Ftaught us.
OL,17,F"Mum's story matters. Her life
OL,18,Fmattered. We ask that anyone who hears
OL,19,Fher story helps us keep her name and
OL,20,Fmemory alive."
