OL,5,CLeicester
OL,7,FA man has been charged with the murder
OL,8,Fof Nila Patel.
OL,10,FMichael Chuwuemeka, 23, of Dover
OL,11,FStreet, Leicester has also been
OL,12,Fcharged with dangerous driving,
OL,13,Fpossession with intent to supply class
OL,14,FB drugs, attempted grievous bodily
OL,15,Fharm relating to an incident on
OL,16,FWelford Road prior to the collision
OL,17,Fand assault of an emergency worker
OL,18,Ffollowing an alleged assault on a
OL,19,Fpolice officer after his arrest.
