OL,7,FChuwuemeka has also been charged with
OL,8,Fcausing actual bodily harm in
OL,9,Fconnection with a separate victim in
OL,10,FLondon in the early hours of Tuesday,
OL,11,F24 June.
OL,13,FChuwuemeka appeared via video link at
OL,14,FLeicester Crown Court sitting at
OL,15,FLoughborough on Tuesday, July 1, where
OL,16,Fhe was further remanded into custody.
